HEADWORD: Cyclopterus
<hw>Cyclopterus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the type genus of the
<fam>Cyclopteridae</fam>, consisting of lumpfishes. It includes
<spn>Cyclopterus lumpus</spn> of the North Atlantic.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Cyclopterus</gen>.</syn>⟦br⟧
